Package: pdindicatoR
Title: pdindicatoR: Calculate and Visualize a Phylogenetic Diversity Indicator 
    based on species occurence data cubes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lissa", "Breugelmans", "lissa.breugelmans@plantentuinmeise.be", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID")),
    person("Maarten", "Trekels", , "maarten.trekels@plantentuinmeise.be", role = c("aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID")),
    person("Louise", "Hendrickx", , "louise.hendrickx@plantentuinmeise.be", role = c("aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID")))
Description: A package to calculate and produce a map of phylogenetic diversity 
    scores for each grid cell in the input species occurences data cube, and 
    calculate the percentage of high PD cells within currently protected areas. 
    You provide a phylogenetic tree, the datacube for the corresponding species 
    is downloaded from GBIF (or user-uploaded), and the package does the rest.
